videos.headline: Aidan O'Connell lets it fly for 53-yard Purdue TD
videos.description: Aidan O'Connell airs it out to Milton Wright for a 53-yard Boilermaker touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Aidan O'connell throws 53-yard TD Pass vs. Northwestern) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Northwestern finds pay dirt as time expires in the half
videos.description: Andrew Marty finds Marshall Lang for a 4-yard Wildcats touchdown, putting Northwestern on the board as time expires for the half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Andrew Marty throws 4-yard touchdown Pass vs. Purdue) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Milton Wright hauls in his second receiving TD
videos.description: Aidan O'Connell finds Milton Wright for the duo's second pitch-and-catch touchdown to extend the Boilermakers lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Milton Wright hauls it in for 17-yard Receiving touchdown) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Evan Hull punches it in for a Northwestern TD
videos.description: Evan Hull keeps his feet moving and forces his way into the end zone for a Wildcats touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Touchdown! Evan Hull scores vs. Purdue) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Purdue's Aidan O'Connell connects with Milton Wright for their 3rd TD
videos.description: Aidan O'Connell airs it out to Milton Wright for the duo's third touchdown of the game.
